===Noun===

#{{linguistics}}: A process of [[neologism]] whereby a word is formed through an incorrect [[morphological]] division.

::''example'': The word ''editor'' was incorrectly thought to be a [[root]] ''edit'' + a [[suffix]] ''-or'' when in fact it is a single [[morpheme]].


